Task 1 - 
1. Application ko server pe run karna hai 
EC2 - Server (Linux)
2. sudo yum install httpd
3. EC2 ke SG me Port 80(Inbound)
4. public IP ko web browser se open kiya
5. cd /var/www/html
6. vi index.html -> content daal diya
7. web me IP ko open kiya 

Task 2 -

1. EC2 par docker install 
2. sudo chmod 777 /var/run/docker.sock
3. docker images 
4. docker pull nginx - it has only downloaded docker image of nginx on your EC2.
5. docker run -dit -p 8080:80 nginx  - run the image of nginx
6. Open with EC2 IP:8080   [8080 is a container port]

Application(HTML) - > Web server -> Server 



